{
  "id": "adv_card_hrk_02_03",
  "title": "佐伯遙子 3話 夜の浜辺で",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――サニーピースの沖縄ライブ当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—The day of the Sunny Peace Okinawa concert",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_03-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "夏といえば水遊び！\n思いっきり水を浴びて盛り上がりましょう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Summer means splashing in the ocean!\nLet’s have fun in the water!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.366666666666666,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2966.666666666668,
          "startTime": 9.333333333333334
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_03-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "私がみんなに水をかけちゃうわよ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m going to splash you all!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.266666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_03-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "暑い夏の野外ライブ！\nずぶ濡れになってもみんなの熱気は冷めないわよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A hot summer outdoor concert!\nYou can’t put out these flames‚ not with an entire ocean!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.766666666666666,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2933.3333333333335,
          "startTime": 19.7
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_03-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "水をかけてほしい人は手を挙げて！\n狙い撃ちしちゃうわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Anyone who wants to get splashed‚ raise your hand!\nI’ll be aiming straight for you!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.6,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 24.2
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3299.9999999999973,
          "startTime": 27.9
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawastage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 27.633333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ファンの熱気で会場は大盛り上がりだ\n今日のライブは大成功だな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The venue is blazing with intensity from the fans.\nThis concert is a scorcher‚ no doubt!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.4,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5466.666666666669,
          "startTime": 38.86666666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawastage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 36.46666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_03-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "みんなで真夏の海を楽しむわよ！\nまだまだ夏は終わらないんだから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let’s enjoy the summer ocean together!\nThe heat isn’t over yet!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.9,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4000,
          "startTime": 43.9
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 43.63333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 43.63333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_03-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "ん～、夜の浜辺っていいわね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mmm! The beach at night is so nice!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.833333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 49.766666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "行きたい廃墟があるって言ってたのに\n急にどうしたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought you wanted to visit some ruins.\nWhat happened?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.666666666666664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 54.666666666666664
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_03-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "気が変わったの。だってせっかく沖縄に来たのに\n全然海で遊べなかったんだもん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just a change of heart. We came all the way to Okinawa‚\nbut I haven’t had a chance to play at the beach.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.266666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 62.63333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_03-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "沖縄の海を眺めながら散歩するのもいいでしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let’s take a walk while looking at the ocean.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.63333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 66.73333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_03-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "ライブが終わったら私のお願いを何でも聞くって\n言ってたんだし、今夜は付き合ってよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You said you’d do whatever I wanted after the concert.\nSo tonight‚ this is what we’re going to do.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.26666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 73.76666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "……遙子さん、沖縄に来る前と比べて\n表情が明るくなりましたね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You seem a lot more cheerful now\nthan you were before we came to Okinawa.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 79.33333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_03-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "……そうね、ライブがうまくいって\n沖縄への苦手意識がやっと克服出来た気がするわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I guess I am. The concert went well.\nI think I’m finally over my Okinawa phobia.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_03-hrk011.m4a",
      "text": "これも{user}君とみんなが\n私を励ましてくれたおかげよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s all thanks to you and the others\ncheering me on.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 92.66666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_03-hrk012.m4a",
      "text": "おかげで野外ライブは大成功\n最高の夏の思い出になったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The outdoor concert was a big success!\nThis is one of my best memories of summer ever.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 98.03333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_03-hrk013.m4a",
      "text": "……ねえ、前にもこうして二人で\n夜の浜辺を歩いたことがあるの、覚えてる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Hey‚ do you remember the two of us\nwalking together down the beach at night?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 105.26666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "覚えてますよ。二人で海を見ながら話をしましたよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I do. We talked while look out at the ocean.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.26666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 110.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_03-hrk014.m4a",
      "text": "私がデビューして間もない頃よね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was soon after my debut.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 113.83333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_03-hrk015.m4a",
      "text": "オーディションに落ちた私が浜辺で落ち込んでいたら\n{user}君が迎えに来てくれたのよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was feeling depressed on the beach after failing an audition.\nYou came to find me‚ {user}.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 120.36666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_03-hrk016.m4a",
      "text": "あの時「諦めないで一緒に頑張っていこう」って\n言ってくれたこと、今でも覚えてるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I still remember what you said to me.\n“Don’t give up. We can do this together.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.83333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_03-hrk017.m4a",
      "text": "それから、サニーピースを結成して間もない頃にも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And then‚ soon after we formed Sunny Peace‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 132.36666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_03-hrk018.m4a",
      "text": "私にミュージカル出演の話が来た時\nアイドルを辞めないように引き留めてくれたよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I got that offer to appear in that musical.\nAnd you were the one who persuaded me to remain an idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.83333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 139.43333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_03-hrk019.m4a",
      "text": "{user}君がいなかったら\n私はどこかでアイドルを諦めていたかもしれない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If it wasn’t for you‚ {user}…\nI would have given up on being an idol long ago.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 145.26666666666668
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_03-hrk020.m4a",
      "text": "今日のライブもそう、{user}君が\n応援してくれたから諦めずにやり遂げられたんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The concert today is part of that too‚ {user}.\nIt was a success because of your ongoing support.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 152.06666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "やり遂げられたのは遙子さんが頑張ったからですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was a success because of your hard work‚ Haruko.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 155.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_03-hrk021.m4a",
      "text": "……沖縄での初ライブに失敗して落ち込んでいた\n昔の私に教えてあげたいわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I wish I could send a message back in time\nto myself after the last Okinawa blowout.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 159.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_02_03-hrk022.m4a",
      "text": "数年後、あなたの歌とパフォーマンスで\n沖縄の人達を笑顔にするんだよって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’d let her know that‚ in just a few more years‚\nher singing and dancing would bring smiles to Okinawa.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 170.06666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
