      "text": "どうしてかしら。{user}君が相手だと\n言わなくていいことまでつい話しちゃうのよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You have a strange power‚ {user}.\nI feel so open around you‚ I always say too much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 186.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
