      "text": "ええ。でも星見市にあって東京の寮にないものが\n一つだけあるのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. But there’s one thing missing in Tokyo that we had in Hoshimi.\nJust one thing I can think of.",
        "id": ""
