      "text": "海よ。考え事をする時よく海岸を散歩していたから\n寮の近くに海がないのは少し寂しいわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The ocean. I would always walk on the beach while thinking.\nIt’s a bit sad that our current dorm isn’t close to the sea.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 232.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
